<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>Quantify your life</h1>
  <p class="lead">This is an experimental project to facilitate obsessively recording information about your life</p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <h2>The Pitch</h2>
    <p>The initial idea of this project was just to provide a simple mechanism to capture the timestamp as activities are started and finished</p>
    <p>Various graphs and charts will appear over time to try to assist in interpreting and analysing this informtation</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span3 well">
    <h3>Step 1</h3>
    <p>Create a <a href="https://browserid.org">browserid</a> account associated with your email address and log in</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span3 well">
    <h3>Step 2</h3>
    <p>Install the <a href="/AndnowDroid.apk">android client</a> application and configure your API token</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span3 well">
    <h3>Step 3</h3>
    <p>Start timing/counting anything you think might reveal interesting information</p>
  </div>
</div>

