<div class="row">
  <div class="span2 offset1">
    <p>You may prefer to deploy your own instance of this application</p>
    <p>It's really simple to get an instance up and running in heroku in a few short steps</p>
  </div>
  <div class="span5">
    <pre>
    git clone git://github.com/markryall/andnow_rails.git
    cd andnow_rails
    bundle
    heroku apps:create -s cedar
    git push heroku master
    heroku run rake db:migrate
    </pre>
